header: ['BMW to begin gradual restart in San Luis Potosi, Mexico on May 27']
article content: ['MEXICO CITY (Reuters) - German carmaker BMW said on Tuesday it would begin a gradual restart of operations at its plant in the central Mexican state of San Luis Potosi on Wednesday, May 27. ', 'The company made the announcement in a statement to Reuters. ', 'Reporting by Sharay Angulo']
